2026-04-14 | Remove All Spaces from String

	Question
Return string after removing all spaces.

	Approach
1.	Traverse the string character by character  
2.	If character is not a space:
		add it to result  
3.	Skip spaces  

	Time Complexity
	O(n)

	Space Complexity
	O(n)

	Solution

class Solution {
public:
    string removeSpaces(string s) {

        string result = "";

        for(char c : s){
            if(c != ' ')
                result += c;
        }

        return result;
    }
};

	Key Insight
Simply filter out unwanted characters (spaces).  
This is a straightforward **linear traversal problem**.
